{"tid":1642532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經濟戰咁簡單易做又低風險的點解唔做盡佢","createTime":"2019-10-09T17:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T06:53:25.000Z","uid":132217,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7e6c69ceeb516a0c3aeb5d8ac2c951c861a9426e","tid":1642532,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:59:54.000Z","msg":"我知好多人做緊啦，但唔夠大家好似做主線咁做呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要影響埋身邊的人！<br />\n<br />\n呢條戰線受惠予香港的租金貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，旅遊業傾斜內地客等問題，少少毛利的下跌可做成盈利的大跌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/2701324926545942/?ref=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F2701324926545942%2F%3Fref%3Dshare&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX59g1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=e94cf076\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/2701324926545942/?ref=share</a><br />\n<br />\n輕輕一做就已經又發盈警又執笠啦。另一方面有龍門，加籐屋做到笑個D，香港人大把人窮得只剩下錢。而且對家係吹我地唔漲呀！<br />\n<br />\n聚所9知對家想做的就係用紅色資金全面統戰，敵人都想爭住做的事，就代表我地做啱左。<br />\n<br />\n聽日雙十感謝日過後呢條線大家要全面生活化同長期化。<br />\n<br />\n如果學生宣傳方向係向大人呼籲：<br />\n我們願意為你擋子彈，你們可以行遠少少唔買Starbucks （whatever 深藍店）嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我見到的係好多5毛就擺買行動開始帶風向，扮中立，扮死狗等，佢地真係開始驚。<br />\n<br />\n黃色生態圈<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/2701324926545942/?ref=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F2701324926545942%2F%3Fref%3Dshare&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX59g1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=e94cf076\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/2701324926545942/?ref=share</a><br />\n<br />\n得80k ，要推多d 人入，search 店好方便<br />\n<br />\nOpenrice <br />\n有個叫Hker2019 的account ，入面收集左1200間食店左右。search by 距離都好方便。<br />\n<br />\n雙十後支線力推呢條線！香港人最善忘同貪方便，要令用黃色生態圈變得方便係而家架啦！！！<br />\n<br />\n而家唔推等幾時，求手足幫推。可能有手足係學生覺得呢條線無咩用，但好多和理非戴個罩都驚的時候，有d 手足真係窮得只剩下錢，亦有中年人自覺負左下一代的未來，但係又肴底唔上街，比佢地一個補償的機會好嗎？呢條線又簡單，仲要係贏硬架。咩都試下好唔好！"},{"pid":"60c100988d308cd1827901faae8f550ce0f122fc","tid":1642532,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:01:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23854c8e11db687fcef1980f424249592b977415","tid":1642532,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:01:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d414cc1e709585c9e2d267cfed4a2ede8d84793","tid":1642532,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:01:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d0ff7b0e77813c0eb52aa1d726312aa900ae55c","tid":1642532,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:04:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c515b07ad8df6d68bfd462cd0c5aef8e99ba6c","tid":1642532,"uid":150742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:11:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/free-hong-kong-tshirts-on-nba-opening-night?fbclid=IwAR1qRUFOYUqnZXYZt9YxPl2WCIio1Q_oz29gN7IfJHeSnvr1wEHcqE05cls\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Ffree-hong-kong-tshirts-on-nba-opening-night%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1qRUFOYUqnZXYZt9YxPl2WCIio1Q_oz29gN7IfJHeSnvr1wEHcqE05cls&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX59g1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=58a9ab6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gofundme.com/f/free-hong-kong-tshirts-on-nba-opening-night?fbclid=IwAR1qRUFOYUqnZXYZt9YxPl2WCIio1Q_oz29gN7IfJHeSnvr1wEHcqE05cls</a><br />\n美國人集資係NBA開幕之夜派&quot;Stand With Hong Kong&quot; T-Shirt俾在場觀眾 搞到到時班大陸人連cap圖都cap唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連豬話你地連Retweet咁簡單都唔做 點光復香港呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://twitter.com/Sun_DMoreyFan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSun_DMoreyFan&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX59g1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=081df6a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Sun_DMoreyFan</a><br />\n呢個係Fundraising Organizer嘅Twitter 大家一齊去Retweet + say thank you to 咁多位 sirs and madams<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d039c8e3bbf5b80a943780cb8c1e9270b835514f","tid":1642532,"uid":224916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T19:27:02.000Z","msg":"Posh"},{"pid":"8f3f93c02288c2aa1097f530768f1ee47e9d248c","tid":1642532,"uid":154892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T19:27:54.000Z","msg":"雙十全力買"},{"pid":"547a4c35c028477ff0595d724894b0d8830484e8","tid":1642532,"uid":200019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T19:30:35.000Z","msg":"我都唔明，遊行咁麻煩，又企又行8個鐘都做<br />\n<br />\n幫襯黃店咁簡單又都有得打卡都咁少人做"},{"pid":"f36604d73af98e3f829f26e900901cd406eba388","tid":1642532,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T06:21:39.000Z","msg":"推呀，唔該大家都幫手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add2534600339e6eb6f89b9da44d68440794fcc8","tid":1642532,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T06:21:57.000Z","msg":"今日雙十全力買呀"},{"pid":"12f7c08935565604590bd20e9685925cbca1bb4f","tid":1642532,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T06:24:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79c34dc48dd8f506dde269ca4b728303dc6dce82","tid":1642532,"uid":30868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T06:33:38.000Z","msg":"日日做緊， 只吃黃店"},{"pid":"b99772126eda40a3a66124a1f44c8dcd6afb8c89","tid":1642532,"uid":238461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T06:53:25.000Z","msg":"在做"}]}